@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}
<div class="container">
    <div class="jumbotron text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4">About Zero Hunger</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="section-content">Zero Hunger is an NGO dedicated to reducing food waste and feeding deprived people, especially children, in Dhaka city. Our mission is to ensure that no food goes to waste when there are hungry people in our community. We believe that every meal can make a difference in someone's life.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="section-title">What We Do</h2>
            <p class="section-content">We work with local restaurants, buffets, offices, community centers, and individuals to collect surplus food before it goes to waste. Our dedicated team of employees and volunteers ensures that the collected food is distributed to those in need. We also educate and raise awareness about food waste and hunger in our community.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Impact</h2>
            <p class="section-content">Since our establishment, we have successfully collected and distributed thousands of meals to deprived individuals and families. Through our efforts, we aim to make a lasting impact on reducing food waste and fighting hunger in Dhaka city. Together, we can create a hunger-free community.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="section-title">Get Involved</h2>
            <p class="section-content">You can join us in our mission to end hunger. Whether you're a restaurant owner, an individual with surplus food, or someone looking to volunteer, your support is valuable. Together, we can make a difference in the lives of those in need. Contact us to learn more about how you can get involved.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/Home/Contact" role="button">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

